<h2 id="call-recording">Call recording</h2>

<p>Calls are recorded for training and quality assurance purposes. Other calls made directly to Companies House may also be recorded for the same purposes. These recordings will be erased 18 months from the date of the call unless there is a business need to retain them. Any such calls will not be retained any longer than is necessary.</p>

<h2 id="office-closures-during-public-holidays">Office closures during public holidays</h2>

<p>Companies House online services are available during public holidays, but our contact centre and helpdesk will be closed.</p>

<p>Our Cardiff office is staffed 24 hours a day, 7 days a week to receive documents delivered by hand or post. The London and Edinburgh offices have a letterbox for out of hours deliveries, but the Belfast office does not.</p>

<div class="call-to-action">
<p>You can <a rel="external" href="https://ewf.companieshouse.gov.uk">file your accounts and annual return online</a>. You’ll need an authentication code, so if you have to <a rel="external" href="https://ewf.companieshouse.gov.uk">request a code</a> allow plenty of time, as they are sent to the company by post.</p>
</div>

